## <a id="limitations"></a>Limitations

<p>The DataStax Enterprise for PCF has the following limitations:</p>

<ul>
<li>It is for development purposes only.
    Users will not receive general support from DataStax if their DataStax Entrprise clusters are provisioned
    using the DataStax Enterprise for PCF during the beta period.</li>
<li>The provisioned DSE clusters do not provide DSE Search, DSE Analytics, and DSE Graph features.</li>
<li>Developers are limited to three service plans.</li>
<li>The DataStax Enterprise for PCF tile can be installed in PCF deployments that run in multiple Availability Zones (AZs).
    However, the DSE service can only provision cluster nodes within a single AZ.</li>
<li>Maximum DSE cluster size is 40.</li>
</ul>

